    <string name="acerca_de_texto">AERIS\n\nThis application has been developed as a project using Android Studio.\n\nAPPLICATION INFORMATION:\n
        • Version: 2.0\n• Developed by: Gabriel Hernández Rodríguez\n\nFEATURES:\n
        • Hourly and daily weather forecast\n• Multiple location management\n
        Detailed information on humidity, wind, UV and precipitation\n
        • Intuitive interface with Material3\n• Multi-language support (Spanish/English)\n
        • Light and dark theme\n• Units customization\n\nTECHNOLOGIES USED:\n
        • Kotlin\n• Jetpack Compose\n• OPEN WEATHER API with Ktor\n• Room Database (SQLite)\n
        • Material3 Components\n• MVVM Architecture\n
        • DataStore Preferences\n• LiveData and Coroutines</string>

